{"tid":840982,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"為何不溫習是件壞事情","createTime":"2018-09-29T08:30:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T13:11:23.000Z","uid":121247,"like":17,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"94e4a5caa14bc388ca477721be68b252ac13b8c7","tid":840982,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:30:26.000Z","msg":"沒有U　這人生被破壞嗎<br />\n無學歷都會溫暖嗎<br />\n和ive仔一起搵工好嗎<br />\n<br />\n若證書　仿似戲劇那樣假<br />\n讀恒大一切都美化<br />\n搭小巴都可以溝女嗎<br />\n<br />\n你說我未能定時<br />\n令你每天pound of一次<br />\n我沒說出一句畢業台詞<br />\n是你心中一種缺陷定義<br />\n流進了眼角裡的刺<br />\n<br />\n為何讀恒大亦是罪名<br />\n為何不溫習是件壞事情<br />\n從來未察覺我每次打波<br />\n去book場　都有半價學生證<br />\n<br />\n為何苦不八大亦是罪名<br />\n為何走後門是件壞事情<br />\n從來未察覺我present 動聽<br />\n在我呼吸聲早已說明<br />\n甚麼都會用一生保證"},{"pid":"89697def8e631c64ef172142ed02f283ca3f1f3f","tid":840982,"uid":206050,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T14:22:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我當年入唔到u都改過呢首"},{"pid":"ec0fa53f63a908029c16e55961a38516c2a4b17a","tid":840982,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"89697def8e631c64ef172142ed02f283ca3f1f3f","tid":840982,"uid":206050,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T14:22:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我當年入唔到u都改過呢首"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T15:42:13.000Z","msg":"Ching sickball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622c73019a5c04d249c7cac376b78a05a2020b66","tid":840982,"uid":71092,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T16:31:01.000Z","msg":"溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e14fb3d2b17f722d0159990b619b38d2a6603fe","tid":840982,"uid":101237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T17:03:40.000Z","msg":"識唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/